content: Welcome all to the Vital Signs stream. Please feel free to ask questions about, voice concerns, or comment about the Vital Signs work going on.
This work is being done by CIMI and sponsored by Patient Care. The PSS for this is at https://confluence.hl7.org/display/CIC/Vital+Signs+PSS
The CI build for the IG is at http://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/cimi-vital-signs/branches/master/index.html

Thanks Nathan for creating this stream. Here are some links that may be useful to track participants and observers over the next couple days:
Track description: https://confluence.hl7.org/display/FHIR/2020-05+Vital+Signs+FHIR+IG+Testing
Track Zoom: https://zoom.us/j/3397689120 339 768 9120 VitalSigns@HL7.org
Connectathon Webinar (general room): https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=https-3A__global.gotowebinar.com_join_1861438407741376527_364908066&d=DwMFaQ&c=iqeSLYkBTKTEV8nJYtdW_A&r=2wh7Wc-GWF21APz9_o1vrLCL5k691K8XxgJOV196N9o&m=pFpVazDnuvof_gTm7JRdlV-IHI9irxC0ZJ4fQTjg8OQ&s=WB5vktcFRIGF0C5jJFS8q0hS9GDyQbT6IaxnmUUdJIo&e=
We will be having a track kick off call tomorrow at 11:30 AM EDT/3:30 PM UTC on the track Zoom.
